metadata.name: Police vs Citizens
metadata.description:
Cinematic City is a collection of photographs and videos captured from various cities, including Buenos Aires, Medellín, Havana, Beirut, and more. 

Using a cinematographic perspective, these images were created out of the organic stories told by humanity across the globe.They are an attempt at documenting an average citizen’s day, rather than capturing a voyeuristic exploration of a new place.
